                       (content-type . "text/plain"))
                    "... contents of file1.txt ...")
              (mime (@ (content-disposition
                        . "attachment; filename=\"file2.gif\"")
                       (content-type . "image/gif")
                       (content-transfer-encoding . "binary"))
